[{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "2493148167513843"}]}, "change_log": "VERSION: 0.40.5.0\nFEATURE: Added level rating screen in Scoreboard.\nFEATURE: Endless mode now shows how long (seconds) player survived.\nFEATURE: Endless mode Leaderboards now show time instead of points.\nFEATURE: Added new Endless mode achievements.\nFEATURE: Endless scoreboard now shows how many obstacles dodged.\nCHANGE: SciFi > Virus02 now clones in a different direction.\nCHANGE: Starting level UI now shows if Endless or Campaign; same with ScoreBoard.\nCHANGE: Aborting Endless level no longer adds score to leaderboard.\nCHANGE: SciFi > Crystal now spawns clones in random directions.\nBUGFIX: ScrapFan clones now separate correctly.\nBUGFIX: Maximum obstacle speed correctly implemented for endless mode and custom level files.\nBUGFIX: Closest possible dodge distance is now 0.01 instead of 0.\nBUGFIX: Clones launched from 45-degree portals now slide correctly to position relative to parent.\nBUGFIX: Achievement Unlocked description no longer chops text in 2nd line.\nBUGFIX: Pressing Settings > Reset or Player > Reset buttons now return to Main Menu after resetting settings.", "created_date": 1732393705, "id": "8037774402990736", "version": "0.40.5.0", "version_code": 603, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "5477835475651321", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8043611465740363"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "2493148167513843"}]}, "change_log": "FEATURE: Added new SciFi Campaign #2 levels 5-8 and Bonus #2; all other levels should no longer cause errors but are still WIP.\nBUGFIX: Some obstacles now no longer collide with some types or all other obstacles.\nCHANGE: Increased time of Achievement Unlocked pop-up to 5 seconds.\nCHANGE: SciFi > TrashBag now explodes into trash. The player can not dodge this trash and it causes no harm.\nCHANGE: Replaced SciFi > Scrap1 with new ScrapPipe; now \"boomerangs\" back from platform edge.\nCHANGE: Replaced SciFi > Scrap2 with new ScrapFan which rotates very quickly.\nCHANGE: Obstacles now allowed to target player lower.", "created_date": 1730928916, "id": "7946119265489584", "version": "0.40.4.0", "version_code": 601, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "5477835475651321", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8043611465740363"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "2493148167513843"}]}, "change_log": "FEATURE: Added achievement for when player is hit by all SciFi or Pirates obstacles at least once.\nFEATURE: Added achievement for achieving various scores upon successfully completing a level.\nBUGFIX: Multiple achievements are now queued and displayed one after another.\nBUGFIX: Campaign level score data now saved with correct prefix.\nBUGFIX: SciFi > Barrier now collides with environment and player correctly.\nCHANGE: Reduced size of Pirates > TreasureChest.\nCHANGE: SciFi > Crystal now always creates multiple clones after teleporting.", "created_date": 1730162932, "id": "7897287553706089", "version": "0.40.3.0", "version_code": 599, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}]}}, "viewer": {"user": null}}}